## ğŸŒŸ Features

- ğŸ” Discover hyper-local restaurants and food vendors
- ğŸ›’ Order and send meals to others
- ğŸ” User login and secure authentication
- ğŸ“± Fully responsive UI (mobile & desktop)
- ğŸ’¸ Budget-friendly meals and transparent pricing

